summary: This document consists of multiple TD Bank responses to subpoenas for financial records related to specific account numbers. The bank indicates which documents were provided and which were not found for the period January 1, 2019 to August 19, 2019. The responses are standard bank compliance records showing document production in response to legal requests.

events.title: Subpoena Scope Period
events.description: The time period covered by the subpoena requests for bank records from TD Bank.

keyFacts: TD Bank responded to multiple subpoenas for financial records covering the period January 1, 2019 to August 19, 2019.
The bank provided some documents including bank affidavits, signature cards/online agreements, and statements, but many requested items were not found.
One account number is partially visible as 'sv 4789194481' while others appear redacted or abbreviated.
The bank reserved the right to supplement its response if additional responsive documents are identified.
The document shows standard bank compliance procedures in response to legal subpoenas during an investigation.
